  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415850/extras/9de51a6747368c9fe2459dfafe559803.webp?t=1768575995\" width=532 height=48 /></span><br>Kyuuhei Inui has never been one to take rumors as anything but that - rumors, until his best friend had died while playing the game...<br><br>Kyuuhei is driven to find out the truth behind his friend's mysterious death by any means possible.<br>After exhausting all ideas, he decided the only way to find out the truth is to play <strong>BAD END</strong> himself.<br><br>Will Kyuuhei risk his life to get to the bottom of the game's mystery or will he meet his demise?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415850/extras/6f8b6fc88e93231c64a848321a2ddb3a.webp?t=1768575995\" width=532 height=48 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Drastic short story that will branch according to your \"choice\".<br></li><li>Surprising ending included!<br></li><li>Do not forget \"CG Mode\" and \"Music Mode\" after playing.<br></li><li>Comfortable playing environment by game engine <strong>ADV+++</strong>, specialized in VN games.</li></ul>",
